Comment: 0,0:09:11.92,0:09:12.80,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（片山）うっ…
Comment: 0,0:09:12.88,0:09:13.92,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,うわっ！
Comment: 0,0:09:16.97,0:09:20.14,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（春希）フウ… フウ…
Comment: 0,0:09:20.68,0:09:23.47,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,フウ… フウ…
Comment: 0,0:09:24.06,0:09:27.02,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（深呼吸）
Comment: 0,0:09:27.31,0:09:28.31,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,はっ！
Comment: 0,0:09:29.48,0:09:30.40,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,はああっ！
Comment: 0,0:09:30.48,0:09:32.32,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（人食いのうめき声）
